\\subsection\{Theoretical framework and origins\}\
This part will aim to give the reader an insight into the factors that triggered this change. It will develop the events related to the subprime crisis coupled with the scandal related to the manipulation of LIBOR; two major events that have made a great echo on the world financial markets.\\newline\
